Industry News


                Health Care            


Memphis medical device company gets $725K in seed funding




Apr 17, 2017, 12:30pm CDT






Industries & Tags


                    Health Care,                 


            Medical Devices             














Elle Perry


Digital Producer
Memphis Business Journal













                    Share
                


























 Order Reprints


 Save Article




